===Noun===
{{en-noun|rain|rains}}
#[[Category:Weather]] {{uncountable}} Condensed [[water]] falling from a [[cloud]].
#{{uncountable}} {{figurative}} Any matter moving or falling, usually through air, and especially if liquid or otherwise figuratively identifiable with [[raindrop]]s.
#{{countable}} {{figurative}} An instance of [[particle]]s or larger pieces of [[matter]] moving or [[fall]]ing through [[air]].
#:''A rain of mortar fire fell on our trenches.''
